data.text: The show would last 178 episodes over eight seasons. Doherty would leave after the third season and be replaced with Rose McGowan. https://t.co/vvnxsIFh3p
Producer Aaron Spelling liked to brag about how the network renewed the series for a second season after just the second episode had aired. https://t.co/NGfD0sj06x
Three sisters discover a book in the attic of their old family home that reveals they are powerful witches tasked with protecting the world from supernatural threats. https://t.co/bLOAWfChJR
